---
source: crates/opencode-cli/tests/cli_help_snapshots.rs
expression: "render_help(&[\"opencode\", \"serve\", \"--help\"])"
---
Start the HTTP API server in headless mode. Bind precedence: CLI > resolved config > defaults

Usage: opencode serve [OPTIONS]

Options:
      --host <HOST>  Bind host override (CLI > resolved config > defaults)
  -p, --port <PORT>  Bind port override (CLI > resolved config > defaults)
  -h, --help         Print help
